User Story:

"As a visitor, I want to register for an account using a username and password so that I can post reviews and rate movies"
Error message if duplicate usernames. 
Successful login/registration redirects to login page.
Priority: 13.3 (Low-priority)

"As a registered user, I want to be able to login so that I can access my account and review movies."
Invalid Credentials drop an error message
Successful login redirects to home or movies webpage.
Priority: 40 (Average) 

"As a visitor, I want to be able to browse the movie selections and look at info about each specific movie"
Get a list of available Movies 
Retrieve database information  about each specific movie
Priority: 23.3 (Average)

"As a user, I want to write and submit a review with a rating (1-5 stars) so that I can share my opinion on a movie."
Reviews must include a rating and optional comment.
Users cannot post multiple reviews for the same movie.
Priority: 140 (High-priority) 

"As a user, I want to see all the reviews a specific user has made"
Persist a database with users review
Select a user and get all the reviews 
Priority: 7 (Low-priority) 

"As a user, I want to edit or delete my review so that I can correct or remove my opinion at a later time" 
Allow author to edit/delete review
Change updates immediately in movies review list
Priority: 75 (High-priority)
